    "ArticleTitle": "Borrelia burgdorferi OspC protein required exclusively in a crucial early stage of mammalian infection.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "3554",
      "EndPage": "3564",
      "MedlinePgn": "3554-64"
